txt.en: 'That young wood-cutter's in for nothing but trouble, going into the Old Forest like that.'
'The season is treating us very well. There'll be plenty of feasting this winter!'
'Celandine's brother, Doderic, has gone off missing again. It's that Merry Brandybuck's fault, mark my words!'
'It's true, you won't find me going anywhere near Crickhollow. Not after what happened the other day!'
